\b0 \cf2 Static Shielding Bags (SSB), also known as ESD Shielding Bags or Anti-Static Shielding Bags, are specially designed to protect\
sensitive electronic components from electrostatic discharge (ESD), static electricity, dust, and handling damage during storage and\
transportation.\
SSB bags are widely used in Semiconductor Packaging, PCB Packaging, HDD, IC, and other Static Sensitive Component\
Packaging applications where reliable ESD protection is essential.\
Manufactured using conductive and static shielding materials, our SSB products provide effective protection for electronic\
devices while supporting cleanroom and industrial packaging requirements. As a trusted provider of ESD Packaging Solutions and\
Cleanroom Packaging, SKY United Industrial (Thailand) Co., Ltd. manufactures high-quality Anti-Static Bag in Thailand with stable\
quality, fast lead time, and cleanroom production standards.\
